(5, 'about', 'We were talking about the new movie.', 'Estávamos falando sobre o novo filme.', '/wiː wɜːr ˈtɔːkɪŋ əˈbaʊt ðə nuː ˈmuːvi/'),
(6, 'above', 'The bird flew above the trees and disappeared into the sky.', 'O pássaro voou acima das árvores e desapareceu no céu.', '/ðə bɜːd fluː əˈbʌv ðə triːz ənd ˌdɪsəˈpɛəd ˈɪntuː ðə skaɪ/'),
(7, 'abroad', 'They decided to study abroad for a year.', 'Eles decidiram estudar no exterior por um ano.', '/ðeɪ dɪˈsaɪdɪd tuː ˈstʌdi əˈbrɔːd fɔːr ə jɪər/'),
(8, 'absence', 'Her absence from the meeting was noticed by everyone.', 'A ausência dela na reunião foi notada por todos.', '/hɜːr ˈæbsəns frəm ðə ˈmiːtɪŋ wəz ˈnəʊtɪst baɪ ˈɛvrɪwʌn/'),
