(10, 'absolute', 'She has absolute control over the situation.', 'Ela tem controle absoluto sobre a situação.', '/ʃiː hæz ˈæbsəluːt kənˈtrəʊl oʊvər ðə ˌsɪtʃʊˈeɪʃən/'),
(11, 'absolutely', 'I absolutely agree with your opinion.', 'Eu concordo absolutamente com a sua opinião.', '/aɪ ˈæbsəluːtli əˈɡriː wɪð jɔːr əˈpɪnɪən/'),
(12, 'absorb', 'The sponge can absorb a lot of water.', 'A esponja pode absorver muita água.', '/ðə spʌndʒ kæn əbˈzɔːrb ə lɒt əv ˈwɔːtər/'),
