(71, 'advice', 'He gave me some valuable advice about my career.', 'Ele me deu alguns conselhos valiosos sobre minha carreira.', '/hiː ɡeɪv miː sʌm ˈvæljuəbl ædˈvaɪs əˈbaʊt maɪ kəˈrɪə/'),
