(73, 'affair', 'The meeting was an important affair for the company.', 'A reunião foi um evento importante para a empresa.', '/ðə ˈmiːtɪŋ wəz ən ɪmˈpɔːtənt əˈfɛə fɔːr ðə ˈkʌmpəni/'),
