(86, 'agent', 'The real estate agent showed us several houses.', 'O corretor de imóveis nos mostrou várias casas.', '/ðə rɪəl ɪsˈteɪt ˈeɪdʒənt ʃoʊd ʌs ˈsɛvrəl ˈhaʊzɪz/'),
